source.name: OASAS Trended Medicaid Recipient Summary Profile
source.description: This profile shows the services received by Medicaid recipients, recipient counts, paid claim dollars, and claim amounts for each main type of Medicaid chemical dependence services and for non-chemical dependence services received by the chemical dependence cohort.
